    "gp_section_561330759474873429": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "0bbf03bd0e03f9f2aca60940f226fbb38cab02bf81e4ba69abcaa7dbed1839f6_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg0045cZav__text": "<p>And until you rehydrate your spinal discs, the pain will never truly go away.</p>",
        "gg4YoJ0BCta_text": "<p>When at full height, you should be able to move and bend without any issues, and your discs should be able to absorb any impact with ease.</p>",
        "ggGkzemG1js_text": "<span style=\"color:#055BDC;\"><strong>You Are Just 15-Minutes Away From Being FREE of Stabbing Back Pain</strong></span>",
        "ggN5O792d2I_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/560e1b00e09a4822b3dd9099f72c91b8.mp4",
        "ggN5O792d2I_poster_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-cb6ab29a-5399-4688-b30b-bbc4cecace4c.png",
        "ggN5O792d2I_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggN5O792d2I_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggQAm8x-ujQ_text": "<p>But imagine, as we sit for prolonged periods, work long hours, and grow older…</p>",
        "ggRTR9XYKM9_text": "<p>Our discs dry out and shrink, forcing the vertebrae closer together and putting pressure on the nerves.</p>",
        "ggWQIG9fsLw_text": "If You Want To Relieve Sciatica And Back Pain… You Must Start With Your Spinal Discs",
        "ggWaLe4w3DQ_text": "<p>This is the root cause of Sciatica and the leading reason why back pain and stiffness feel never ending.</p>",
        "ggj3LHKR5Jp_text": "<p>Your spinal discs act as the shock absorbers between your vertebrae, cushioning your spine and protecting your nerves.</p>",
        "ggymlr3ksYA_text": "If You Want To Relieve Sciatica And Back Pain… You Must Start With Your Spinal Discs"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-561330759474873429"
    },
    "gp_section_561330759474938965": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "b12c0a4bf767eec136e56c6b4a9e0a05decc7d6534f7b7a390ea4661c0c3d28a_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg0znNmAU8T_text": "<p><strong>Improved mobility and less pain</strong></p>",
        "gg3GwCpV-GT_text": "<p><strong>Freedom from discomfort in your back and legs&nbsp;</strong></p>",
        "gg5A_s7vPft_text": "<p>Users are reporting significant improvements after just a few sessions! And almost everyone continues using it daily.</p>",
        "gg6lqX8ncBw_text": "Professionally Designed &amp; Recommended",
        "gg9L3EDUCMV_text": "The Perfect Therapy Every Time",
        "ggGQXnMY5zT_text": "The Perfect Therapy Every Time&nbsp;",
        "ggOLny2Lf9H_text": "<p><strong>Better nights of sleep feeling more rested</strong></p>",
        "ggSvIZrM2QP_text": "<p><strong>Boosted confidence while walking and standing</strong></p>",
        "ggTX3oVSncW_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine \"Triple Fusion\" Massager has been designed alongside leading spine specialists as an effective way to get relief from back pain and Sciatica.</p>",
        "ggW6FuzFFTV_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/b7221154784149ef88a1a4ed183ca2bf.mp4",
        "ggW6FuzFFTV_poster_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-f4168f84-60f8-43e4-a2ce-1927cf520f17.png",
        "ggW6FuzFFTV_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggW6FuzFFTV_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggYhZQDCRPW_text": "<p>In just 15 minutes a day, you can give yourself another shot at a normal, comfortable life.</p>",
        "ggaFHF5sugD_text": "<p>This means that within a few days of using the<strong> SmoothSpine™ \"Triple Fusion\" Massager</strong>, you can expect to start noticing:</p>",
        "ggcllM8jPEK_text": "<p>For less than 1/3 of the cost of a single therapy session, you can get results that last a lifetime.</p>",
        "ggiVlsgDWSA_text": "<p>Physical therapists and spine specialists aren't always within reach and can be very expensive.&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggihBBrHnWy_text": "<p><strong>The Entire Country Is Raving About the SmoothSpine™ \"Triple Fusion\" Massager!</strong></p>",
        "ggihisY810h_text": "Professionally Designed &amp; Recommended",
        "ggr9awOTvod_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/0c82734003f546349dd4f4973892f5d3.mp4",
        "ggr9awOTvod_poster_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-2a6a94d0-4336-4d76-b84e-87225ce357b8.png",
        "ggr9awOTvod_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggr9awOTvod_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-561330759474938965"
    },
    "gp_section_561330759475004501": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "2735891062ba1c6aa05342a987d33e395eab8ac449528f0e53630a615cdbb93b_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg5779-Q2LD_text": "<p>No, you don’t need to worry about batteries! The SmoothSpine™ Triple Fusion Massager comes with a plug-in power cord, ensuring consistent and uninterrupted therapy without the hassle of recharging or replacing batteries. We recommend using a power source with a minimum of 5V 2A or above for optimal performance.</p>",
        "ggBJa8Yn5GB_text": "Frequently Asked Questions",
        "ggGBgdMGN1b_text": "<p>No need to rush - we ‘ve got your comfort covered. A mere 15 minutes a day with SmoothSpine™ Triple Fusion Massager is all it takes. It’s like having a personal physical therapist, ready to relieve your back whenever you need it.</p>",
        "ggJ59b-ywE__text": "<p>Absolutely! SmoothSpine™ Triple Fusion Massager is your key to relief from Sciatica, back pain, and disc discomfort. Thanks to its innovative \"Triple Fusion\" technology combining dynamic traction, target point massage, and soothing heat therapy.</p>",
        "ggOF78_pLax_text": "<p>Get ready for rapid relief! Many users report feeling noticeable improvements after just one session. For long-term relief, regular use is key. SmoothSpine™ Triple Fusion Massager ensures continuous comfort and relief by targeting the root cause of back pain.</p>",
        "ggZ3I5t3Bhg_text": "<p>If you don’t get the results you want in 90 days or less—we don’t want your money! We are confident that our products work and encourage you to try them risk-free. If you’re not satisfied and wish to return the product, you can do so within our 90-day money-back guarantee.&nbsp;</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_0": "<p>Will SmoothSpine™ Triple Fusion Massager Provide Relief From My Sciatica and Back Pain?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_1": "<p>How Soon Will I Notice Results with SmoothSpine™ Triple Fusion Massager?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_2": "<p>What's the Ideal Duration for Each SmoothSpine™ Triple Fusion Massager Therapy Session?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_3": "<p>Do I need to buy batteries?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_4": "<p>What are the dimensions of the SmoothSpine™ Triple Fusion Back Massager?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_5": "<p>What is your return policy?</p>",
        "ggrcqOh_tmz_text": "<p>The massager measures <strong>23.6\" (L) × 9.8\" (W) × 4.7\" (H)</strong>. It’s perfectly sized to support your lower back while lying on your bed, couch, or floor—large enough for full coverage, but compact enough to store easily. <i>(For international customers: 60 cm × 25 cm × 12 cm)</i><br><i>Please note: Exact size may vary slightly due to the handcrafted nature of production.</i></p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-561330759475004501"
    },
    "gp_section_561330759475070037": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "e8f9cc00baff8290303ce119df4ac6874004332a7fbf34c6422cd2d19b2c8f71_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg9sfrUDNiv_text": "How SmoothSpine “Triple Fusion” Massager Works",
        "ggFoLsfJU5j_text": "<p>The best part about the SmoothSpine™ Massager is that it’s <strong>so simple to use.</strong></p>",
        "ggLpXZltW4C_text": "<p>The second step is to <strong>position SmoothSpine under your lower back</strong> and then use the button controls to start the program of traction, heat, and massage. <strong>Lay back and relax while SmoothSpine does its magic.</strong></p>",
        "ggNDYVqN7Gc_text": "How SmoothSpine “Triple Fusion” Massager Works",
        "ggNxAHEd9SQ_text": "<p>First, <strong>no short-lived batteries </strong>- You just plug it in using the cable that arrives together with your order.</p>",
        "ggb3x-tTKfi_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/4b62cf66768542578f49af24488d3063.mp4",
        "ggb3x-tTKfi_poster_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-f94563b9-6efc-4975-b606-a597a008cc19.png",
        "ggb3x-tTKfi_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggb3x-tTKfi_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggd9w5iVAlN_text": "<p>With consistent use, the <strong>damage to your spine can be reversed</strong>, providing long-lasting relief and allowing you to get back to living your life to the fullest without being held back by back pain or Sciatica.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-561330759475070037"
    },
