        "gg4lOxj8MET_text": "<p>\"Didn’t Expect It to Work THIS Well!\"</p>",
        "ggBi7vQvbIj_text": "<p>\"I Can Move Freely Again!\"</p>",
        "ggJ8hCrLXJq_text": "<p>\"Ok, mine got here last week. I was skeptical at first, but after just a few sessions, my stiffness and sciatica pain improved drastically. I used to dread getting out of bed in the morning because of the pain, but now I can move freely again. So easy to use, and the heat feels amazing on my lower back.\"</p>",
        "ggQgcHb_VvV_text": "<p>John D.</p>",
        "ggReBUA1njy_text": "<p>Linda R.</p>",
        "ggZSVoxxXVa_text": "<p>\"I was not expecting this! When I laid down on the smoothspine massager , I could feel my back start to decompress in a good way. The heat and massage combined made a huge difference, and I could actually relax for the first time in months. My wife said I’m walking more upright. Definitely worth it trying!!\"</p>",
