    "gp_section_561330759475790933": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "6f23a581af29423e2ec77e39f84a435b8c881094f73919e5191d8ea815481873_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg1WJODqwGE_text": "<p>SHORT-ACTING, REQUIRES CONSTANT USE</p>",
        "gg1l9ZsD4ZL_text": "Other Pain Relief Methods",
        "gg35L5tHWLl_text": "<p>Which can cause side effects and addiction.</p>",
        "gg6FUm3nxa8_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-23ff5eac-98d6-4932-bb00-6836a417b18e.png",
        "gg6YHdZykSx_text": "SmoothSpine Massager",
        "gg8B9W6Nh6g_text": "<p>Medical professionals are increasingly skeptical of long-term painkiller use.</p>",
        "ggAE6F26brb_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-23ff5eac-98d6-4932-bb00-6836a417b18e.png",
        "ggFlaRsfX_r_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-23ff5eac-98d6-4932-bb00-6836a417b18e.png",
        "ggGTEluwLZX_text": "<p>FAST-ACTING &amp; EFFECTIVE</p>",
        "ggOZidTxPrt_text": "<p>LONG-LASTING RELIEF</p>",
        "ggQzsqtEZek_text": "<p>No need for expensive doctor visits.</p>",
        "ggS6aIr0DXf_text": "<p>QUESTIONED BY DOCTORS</p>",
        "ggU6Cofrkcy_text": "<p>TAKE HOURS TO WORK</p>",
        "ggZWYjcI0Sj_text": "<p>It’s non-addictive, works fast, and actually does GOOD things for your body.</p>",
        "gg_uUJJZYot_text": "<p>DRUG-FREE PAIN RELIEF</p>",
        "ggabMzZulc1_text": "<p>RELY ON DRUGS &amp; CHEMICALS</p>",
        "ggcBzCOcsVE_text": "<p>EASY TO USE AT HOME</p>",
        "ggcFzCiQ6WE_text": "<p>\"Highly recommended to anyone dealing with Sciatica, herniated discs, and back pain.\"</p>",
        "ggcIYxRgigt_text": "<p>BACKED BY EXPERTS</p>",
        "ggchiUpfJH2_text": "The SmoothSpine Massager Is The Safer, Healthier Choice",
        "ggd0hjAxMgS_text": "<p>Works in as little as 15 minutes!</p>",
        "gggZo7nOlQf_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-23ff5eac-98d6-4932-bb00-6836a417b18e.png",
        "ggiY6BubJDN_text": "<p>Painkillers and other methods take hours or even days to show results.</p>",
        "ggjhrjWgMyc_text": "<p>Painkillers also don’t help your mood, your stress or your anxiety.</p>",
        "ggnUORZ6q9u_text": "<p>It’s natural and non-habit-forming.</p>",
        "ggopNT52XXD_text": "<p>Daily use can even completely realign your spine and rehydrate your discs.</p>",
        "ggplNJpBZcA_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-23ff5eac-98d6-4932-bb00-6836a417b18e.png",
        "ggqa-TsithJ_text": "<p>Painkillers wear off quickly, forcing you to take more doses.</p>",
        "ggun2f_DN31_text": "<p>HARMFUL TO YOUR BODY</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-561330759475790933"
    },
    "gp_section_561330759475856469": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "e0857d45587f5eeca1caba70cfec63c3f451f20a6cdabfa02d3120f4638c3c78_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg-RifOCijk_text": "<p>The moment you lay back on the <strong>SmoothSpine \"Triple Fusion\" Massager</strong>, you'll immediately feel the powerful combination of <strong>dynamic traction, target point massage, and soothing heat therapy</strong> working together.</p>",
        "gg4GNxuDqa0_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/d6b555b3f24e4fd2b87985bb36f0c056.mp4",
        "gg4GNxuDqa0_poster_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-0209d18f-e6fa-4597-b98d-4436aad315a8.png",
        "gg4GNxuDqa0_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "gg4GNxuDqa0_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "gg5gEyQLqLG_text": "<p>The <strong>SmoothSpine \"Triple Fusion\" Massager</strong> fully harnesses the power of three advanced therapies to relieve nerve compression, stiffness, and pain in your back and legs.</p>",
        "gg_-bnIX9QK_text": "<p>The best part?</p>",
        "ggclZmxOds__text": "SmoothSpine \"Triple Fusion\" Massager Restores Spinal Disc Hydration and Relieves Pressure on Your Sciatic Nerve",
        "ggjZnI4Pmdn_text": "<p>These three therapies work in perfect harmony to rehydrate your discs and bring lasting relief.</p>",
        "gglNkdnoYHM_text": "<p>You can use it from the comfort of your own home, even in your bed.</p>",
        "ggrYT7cGWvp_text": "<p><strong>Soothing Heat Therapy: </strong>Warms tissues and enhances fluid absorption, accelerating disc rehydration and healing.</p>",
        "ggu6Yd3u6Yx_text": "<p><strong>Dynamic Traction:</strong> Gently stretches and separates your vertebrae, reducing nerve compression and creating space for discs to rehydrate.</p>",
        "ggyZ6Gf5lWo_text": "<p><strong>Target Point Massage:</strong> Targets tight muscles and deep knots, easing tension and improving circulation for faster relief.</p>",
        "ggzRfc3KmKh_text": "SmoothSpine \"Triple Fusion\" Massager Restores Spinal Disc Hydration and Relieves Pressure on Your Sciatic Nerve"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-561330759475856469"
    },
